## Concept Used
Structures
Arrays
Functions
Loops
Conditional statements

## Algorithm (Simple Steps)

Start
Create a structure for student (id, name, marks)
Ask user for number of students
Input student details
Display menu:
Add student
Display students
Search student
Perform selected operation
Repeat until user exits
Stop

